            <heading x="92">Fishing Rods</heading>
            <text>There are four fishing rods introduced by Mariculture, you will need to use them instead of the vanilla if you want to catch any of the Mariculture Fish or Loot. Each fishing rod can use different types of bait, as well as having different durabilities.</text>
        </paragraph>
