    <page>
        <paragraph wrap="220">
            <heading x="86" y="2">Automatic Fisher</heading>
            <text>The automatic fisher is able to do your fishing for you. You need to supply it with RF, a Fishing Rod, and bait that can be used with that fishing rod. The block also needs to be one above a block of water. They will also work above lava in the nether.</text>
        </paragraph>
        <img src="autofisher" x="18" y="150" size="0.45" stretch="1.25"></img>
    </page>
    <page>
        <paragraph wrap="220">
            <text>Only Capacitor and Hyperkinetic upgrades will work with the autofisher. With capacitor upgrades increasing how much of an internal buffer of RF the Autofisher has, and the Hyperkinetic increasing the speed.</text>
        </paragraph>
        <crafting x="18" y="8" size="2">
            <craft1>blank,fish,blank</craft1>
            <craft2>rodWood,plankWood,rodWood</craft2>
            <craft3>logWood,baseWood,logWood</craft3>
            <craftResult>autofisher</craftResult>
        </crafting>
    </page>
